              ]
            }
          ],
          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "The total photoneutron reaction (g,xn) cross sections",
                " were obtained for natural Al, S, Ta, Bi targets from",
                " thresholds  to  30  MeV  by  directly  counting   of",
                " photoneutrons as   a   functions  of  bremsstrahlung",
                " energy.  The (g,2n) reaction cross sections  for  Ta",
                " and  Bi were calculated using the statistical theory",
                " of the GDR states  decay  and  used  to  obtain  the",
                " (g,sn) reaction cross sections for these nuclei."
              ]
            }
          ],
